{"tid":758774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真。香港人入一入","createTime":"2018-07-28T04:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T05:53:10.000Z","uid":110477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e6b6f89fc26517f4137af84a7002dd00d6be7c","tid":758774,"uid":110477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係第四代香港人。太爺係國軍軍官打到香港之後交比英軍再定居，我阿爺係皇家香港警察做警司。入返正題，近日認識咗個朋友喺大陸出世之後成日都話要港獨又要移民咁樣，又成日話人支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係完全唔知點樣回應佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心裏面好想講其實我哋真正嘅土生土長嘅香港人都唔係好鍾意你地啲咁嘅新移民。唔好喺度扮晒野以為有張身分證就可以洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真正嘅香港人係要對香港有付出過先算，例如父母一早由60-70年代已經來到香港定居，為香港發展出咗一分力。sorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372c7b3d8d9b1a3dc7c63d144461975f61256251","tid":758774,"uid":151717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"雖然無講錯，但係有啲尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5db045f25d926b5eae81ab1d4bebbd19d55c79a","tid":758774,"uid":110477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"372c7b3d8d9b1a3dc7c63d144461975f61256251","tid":758774,"uid":151717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"雖然無講錯，但係有啲尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"唔知點同佢解釋"},{"pid":"b1861c74fa105670a0167eb337951e136c1e0277","tid":758774,"uid":151717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5db045f25d926b5eae81ab1d4bebbd19d55c79a","tid":758774,"uid":110477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"372c7b3d8d9b1a3dc7c63d144461975f61256251","tid":758774,"uid":151717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"雖然無講錯，但係有啲尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,